      "value": "<em>Replace this with a proper description.</em>\n<details>\n<summary>Credits and Instructions</summary>\n<h2>Made by Elwin</h2>\n<h3>Requires:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Active Token Effects</li>\n   <li>Elwin Helpers (Enable in Settings)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n<p>This item is used as a factory to create Flame Tongue weapons. Open this item and select its effects tab. \nOpen the weapon to be transformed into a Flame Tongue, then drag drop the 'Flame Tongue' enchantment effect on the target weapon.\nThe enchantment adds an activity to activate/deactivate the flames when equipped and attuned.\nWhen this activity is used, it activates the flames and adds an AE with a light effect or deactivates it.</p></details>",
